{"thag3.5:0.1":"Theragatha 3.5 ","thag3.5:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.5:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.5:0.4":"Matangaputtattheragatha ","thag3.5:1.1":"“Atisitam atiunham, ","thag3.5:1.2":"atisayamidam ahu; ","thag3.5:1.3":"Iti vissatthakammante, ","thag3.5:1.4":"khana accenti manave. ","thag3.5:2.1":"Yo ca sitanca unhanca, ","thag3.5:2.2":"tina bhiyyo na mannati; ","thag3.5:2.3":"Karam purisakiccani, ","thag3.5:2.4":"so sukha na vihayati. ","thag3.5:3.1":"Dabbam kusam potakilam, ","thag3.5:3.2":"usiram munjapabbajam; ","thag3.5:3.3":"Urasa panudissami, ","thag3.5:3.4":"vivekamanubruhayan”ti. ","thag3.5:3.5":"… Matangaputto thero …. "}